/// - soap_del_tt__TimeZone(tt__TimeZone*) deep deletes tt__TimeZone data members, use only on dst after soap_dup_tt__TimeZone(NULL, tt__TimeZone *dst, tt__TimeZone *src) (use soapcpp2 -Ed)
